performances of those aggressive turtles and a rousing musical show 
based on the dick tracy characters 
and sea world is offering an allnew shamu extravaganza with 
two count em two underwater cameras to capture the whale at 
work 
meanwhile the 630 million universal park built on 444 acres 
has had its problems audienceinvolvement shows featuring jaws 
king kong and a san francisco earthquake failed to operate on 
