but too much should not be made of bushs turnaround it may 
sound cynical but politics is one thing the read my lips was 
pure politics and responsible governing is another it certainly 
is in this case 
since he made so much of saying never never never it took a 
considerable amount of courage for bush to change his position 
but the deficit is soaring all this makes it an urgent 
priority to consider taxraising options promises or no bushs 
