<TEXT>
june 28 
jeune afrique paris on press freedom 
what is the african country where the press is the most free 
no its not senegal its south africa shame on us 
what is the middle eastern country where the press is the most 
free this time youve guessed it yes its israel shame on us 
oh i know very well that south africa is ruled by a minority 
based on color that israel is based on religion and that freedom 
of the press in these two countries benefits foremost the ruling 
class but believe me in each of these countries the oppressed 
also benefit from the free circulation of information and ideas 
