transitioned out to make way for new occupants including 
women said judy schutzman the citys codirector of the centers 
ten beds are to be added next month she said 
city officials say the transition means finding housing for the 
men advocates for the homeless are doubtful 
food not bombs a group that feeds the homeless plans to stage 
an allnight protest outside agnos home friday night bringing 
homeless people to the mayors doorstep 
