somewhere between 18 and 25 percent of its gross domestic product 
on military expenditures he told reporters 
and we have problems with the expenditure of somewhere 
between nine and 15 billion a year to support regimes around the 
world that in the past at least have been hostile to the views and 
interests and principles of the united states 
the soviet union unlike the four countries that were added to 
the western aid program wednesday has not asked for western aid 
but the issue of western aid has become linked to efforts to win 
soviet backing for immediate and full membership of a united 
germany in the 16nation north atlantic treaty organization 
wednesdays meeting was attended by officials from poland 
hungary and the four new beneficiary countries 
